    <note>Zhao(1) Lingkuang [14982] SS, 220.16b (PRC ed. 220.6218). He was Zhi Xiwai Zong zhengshi in 1128, the Zhi Nanwai Zong zheng and then prefect of Quanzhou. The only indication of new address is the address of his great grandson, Shixiu [14993], a Yongjia jinshi in 1190. There are, however, a number of other Yongjia jinshi with suggestive generational names. CBD, 4, 3443.</note>
